room_title: Escape room "Death Row" by Escape Zone 60 in Panama City
room_address: 8128 Front Beach Rd. D Panama City Beach, FL 32407
room_description: You and your fellow inmates claim to have been wrongly convicted and sentenced to death row. In the 60 minutes before your execution is carried out, you are left alone with no prison guards in sight. While the guards prep the chair, will you be able to escape Death Row before the warden returns to make you a statistic?
